76
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:35,215
You might be safe, Mom,
but she'll burn down our house!

77
00:03:35,281 --> 00:03:36,516
No need to worry about that.

78
00:03:37,917 --> 00:03:40,320
Sally's been cold lately.

79
00:03:40,386 --> 00:03:41,354
