80
00:03:42,021 --> 00:03:42,956
-What?
-Huh?

81
00:03:43,523 --> 00:03:45,892
That's enough about me.

82
00:03:45,959 --> 00:03:48,094
I don't know what I was thinking.

83
00:03:48,161 --> 00:03:50,196
I swear something like this will

84
00:03:50,263 --> 00:03:51,331
never happen again!

85
00:03:52,865 --> 00:03:54,400
Oh, sure.

86
00:03:57,804 --> 00:03:59,138
