98
00:04:42,248 --> 00:04:45,618
So what should we do with the title?

99
00:04:45,685 --> 00:04:48,121
-The title, huh?
-Yeah.

100
00:04:49,322 --> 00:04:50,523
<i>Another World?</i>

101
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:52,058
So typical.

102
00:04:52,592 --> 00:04:56,029
Right?
Your mom's so cool. She has good taste.

103
00:04:56,095 --> 00:04:58,765
-As expected of a professional.
-Huh?

104
00:04:59,432 --> 00:05:02,635
Like her most recent series,
<i>Umbilical Cord.</i>

105
00:05:02,702 --> 00:05:04,904
So cool!

106
00:05:05,772 --> 00:05:07,707
It got canceled, though.

107
00:05:09,942 --> 00:05:12,812
Speaking of, what does
"umbilical cord" mean?

108
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,047
No way! You don't know?

109
00:05:14,113 --> 00:05:16,282
I'm a manga otaku. I don't read books.

110
00:05:16,349 --> 00:05:18,851
Only comics. I've never read Mom's books.

111
00:05:19,886 --> 00:05:21,220
