112
00:05:21,287 --> 00:05:24,090
Oh, cool. That sounds deep.

113
00:05:25,158 --> 00:05:26,626
Hey, with Jadwiga,

114
00:05:26,693 --> 00:05:30,663
can we make her boobs bigger?

115
00:05:30,730 --> 00:05:32,965
-Just a little bit?
-No.

116
00:05:33,032 --> 00:05:35,868
You don't understand, Minase.

117
00:05:35,935 --> 00:05:38,271
-For men, boobs are everything.
-No.

118
00:05:44,277 --> 00:05:47,213
We're so sorry about this.

119
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,549
What? Wait.

120
00:05:49,615 --> 00:05:50,616
Huh?

121
00:05:51,384 --> 00:05:54,053
You told him what happened?
You told Konishi?

122
00:05:54,654 --> 00:05:56,255
What do you mean?

123
00:05:59,692 --> 00:06:02,028
I'm here to apologize about
the series of events

124
00:06:02,095 --> 00:06:05,631
with <i>Don't Forget Me…</i>

125
00:06:05,698 --> 00:06:08,034
Oh, that one!

126
00:06:08,101 --> 00:06:09,635
I see.

127
00:06:09,702 --> 00:06:11,304
What else is there?

128
00:06:12,405 --> 00:06:14,407
No, don't worry about it.

129
00:06:15,742 --> 00:06:18,311
We got a little too excited about

130
00:06:18,378 --> 00:06:20,279
a big budget film.

131
00:06:20,847 --> 00:06:22,448
We messed up.

132
00:06:23,015 --> 00:06:26,486
We'll follow the original text.
Naoko, the heroine, will die.

133
00:06:26,552 --> 00:06:28,688
They'll rewrite the whole script.

134
00:06:28,755 --> 00:06:30,223
We also made sure

135
00:06:30,289 --> 00:06:33,426
that Yuto understands that as well.

136
00:06:33,493 --> 00:06:35,428
Yeah. Thanks.

137
00:06:36,362 --> 00:06:38,164
This is to apologize for the mess.

138
00:06:38,231 --> 00:06:40,466
No.

139
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:43,136
-Are you flustered?
-No.

140
00:06:43,202 --> 00:06:44,937
-Are you hiding something?
-Nope!

141
00:06:45,004 --> 00:06:46,672
No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no!

142
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:49,876
