in your private lives.

145
00:06:56,449 --> 00:06:57,784
What do you mean?

146
00:06:57,850 --> 00:07:01,554
Why did you say that? If you won't
get involved, don't say anything!

147
00:07:01,621 --> 00:07:03,089
That's why everyone hates you!

148
00:07:03,156 --> 00:07:04,657
There's nothing going on.

149
00:07:04,724 --> 00:07:06,125
Not one bit.

150
00:07:09,629 --> 00:07:13,332
