152
00:07:17,336 --> 00:07:18,838
Alright.

153
00:07:23,709 --> 00:07:27,713
I thought you brought the bean jelly
from Tatsuya to apologize for the kiss.

154
00:07:30,349 --> 00:07:31,317
Though we didn't kiss.

155
00:07:32,785 --> 00:07:34,353
Should I have brought some?

156
00:07:35,087 --> 00:07:36,789
