157
00:07:40,026 --> 00:07:40,993
Oh.

158
00:07:41,994 --> 00:07:44,030
This is Sora's Limoncello.

159
00:07:44,096 --> 00:07:44,964
Oh.

160
00:07:50,603 --> 00:07:53,105
