257
00:12:46,899 --> 00:12:48,434
I never noticed!

258
00:12:48,501 --> 00:12:51,637
You never notice. You're always
only thinking about yourself…

259
00:12:51,704 --> 00:12:54,874
Ouch! According to my speculations,

260
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:58,110
Shunichiro's a pretty handsome guy, right?

261
00:12:58,177 --> 00:13:02,515
He'll probably bring a traditional
Japanese beauty, like Sayuri Yoshinaga.

262
00:13:02,581 --> 00:13:05,084
